Orbital Laser Platform - Rains death from above.
Mortar tank - Advanced long range mobile artillery.
Assault Bot - Armoured with high damage guns and torpedoes. Amphibious. Attacks land and sea.
Economy - Orbital energy generation.
Missile Ship - Long range with radar. High damage anti-air and tactical missiles. Attacks land, sea, air, and orbital targets.

unit.description: Drone Carrier - Builds and launches missile drones at enemies. Attacks land, air and sea targets.
Interplanetary Transport - Builds and launches up to 16 units at once anywhere in the system.
Heavy Tank - Advanced short range, heavily armored vehicle.
Mobile Anti-Nuke - Launches a single anti-nuclear missile.
Siege Bomber - Durable. Slow. Devastating damage. Attacks land and sea targets.
Rolling Fortress - Near invincible. Long range. Heavy damage. Hover. Attacks land and sea targets.
Seismic Titan - Devastating damage to everything nearby. Amphibious. Attacks land, sea, and undersea targets.
Invasion Titan - Can link with a teleporter to send units directly to planet surface. Attacks everything.
Doomsday Titan - Destroys the planet it's built on once finished.
Lightning Titan - Heavy damage over a wide area. Attacks any targets except orbital.
